[Episode 7]

4
00:01:37,780 --> 00:01:38,220
Mom!

5
00:01:38,580 --> 00:01:39,820
Mom, call an ambulance!

6
00:01:39,980 --> 00:01:40,780
Yawang!

7
00:01:41,620 --> 00:01:42,260
Yawang!

8
00:01:54,100 --> 00:01:54,700
Yawang!

9
00:01:55,180 --> 00:01:56,180
Hang in there!

10
00:01:56,340 --> 00:01:57,020
Yawang!

11
00:01:57,020 --> 00:01:57,700
Shu Yawang!

12
00:01:57,700 --> 00:01:58,300
Don't you leave me behind!

13
00:01:58,300 --> 00:01:59,140
Shu Yawang, wake up.

14
00:01:59,340 --> 00:02:00,260
Shu Yawang, don't sleep!

15
00:02:00,580 --> 00:02:01,260
Yawang!

16
00:02:01,860 --> 00:02:02,980
Don't scare me!

17
00:02:02,980 --> 00:02:03,900
Excuse me! Out of the way!

18
00:02:04,340 --> 00:02:05,100
Yawang!

19
00:02:21,540 --> 00:02:22,100
Yawang.

20
00:02:24,580 --> 00:02:25,140
Yawang.

21
00:02:27,060 --> 00:02:28,220
Look at me.

22
00:02:34,020 --> 00:02:34,500
Mom.

23
00:02:37,260 --> 00:02:37,900
Yawang.

24
00:02:40,060 --> 00:02:41,740
You scared me!

25
00:02:43,940 --> 00:02:46,740
When your dad passed away,
I promised him

26
00:02:48,020 --> 00:02:50,380
that I would take care of you.

27
00:02:52,540 --> 00:02:54,380
If anything happens to you,

28
00:02:56,140 --> 00:02:58,460
how am I supposed to carry on?

29
00:03:02,180 --> 00:03:03,420
Mom, I'm sorry.

30
00:03:05,540 --> 00:03:08,180
As long as you're awake...

31
00:03:09,860 --> 00:03:12,140
Don't ever scare me like that again.

32
00:03:14,020 --> 00:03:14,820
Don't cry.

33
00:03:36,900 --> 00:03:38,900
Hopefully your sister
will be better today.

34
00:03:40,020 --> 00:03:41,060
I'm so worried.

35
00:03:44,180 --> 00:03:45,500
Mom, are you alright?

36
00:03:45,780 --> 00:03:47,540
You've been too tired recently.
You have to take care of yourself.

37
00:03:47,540 --> 00:03:48,060
I'm fine.

38
00:03:48,820 --> 00:03:49,460
Don't worry.

39
00:03:50,180 --> 00:03:51,100
For Yawang's sake,

40
00:03:51,620 --> 00:03:52,860
I won't collapse.

41
00:04:01,540 --> 00:04:02,140
You're here.

42
00:04:03,500 --> 00:04:04,100
Where's Shu Yawang?

43
00:04:04,420 --> 00:04:05,420
Isn't she sleeping in there?

44
00:04:05,420 --> 00:04:06,340
No she isn't!

45
00:04:09,820 --> 00:04:10,420
Take this for me!

46
00:04:28,420 --> 00:04:30,500
Do you like the surprise
I prepared for you?

47
00:04:38,060 --> 00:04:38,580
Miss,

48
00:04:39,980 --> 00:04:42,260
don't do it.

49
00:04:47,580 --> 00:04:48,900
I had a daughter.

50
00:04:50,180 --> 00:04:51,300
She was about as old as you.

51
00:04:52,460 --> 00:04:53,900
Unfortunately, she passed away early.

52
00:04:55,100 --> 00:04:57,860
She's my biggest regret.

53
00:04:59,540 --> 00:05:00,500
Everytime I think of her,

54
00:05:01,900 --> 00:05:03,220
my heart hurts.

55
00:05:05,540 --> 00:05:07,500
Your mother must be
a little younger than me.

56
00:05:09,100 --> 00:05:11,420
You don't want your mother

57
00:05:11,820 --> 00:05:14,260
to live in regret like me
for the rest of her life, right?

58
00:05:24,980 --> 00:05:25,500
Shu Yawang!

59
00:05:27,980 --> 00:05:28,540
Ya!

60
00:05:31,940 --> 00:05:32,580
Yawang!

61
00:05:33,820 --> 00:05:34,340
Come down.

62
00:05:36,180 --> 00:05:37,100
Come down.

63
00:05:49,020 --> 00:05:49,820
Yawang!

64
00:05:50,780 --> 00:05:52,180
You scared me.

65
00:05:56,620 --> 00:05:57,260
Don't do this

66
00:05:57,500 --> 00:05:59,900
ever again, alright?

67
00:06:00,140 --> 00:06:00,740
Mom.

68
00:06:01,780 --> 00:06:02,340
Mom.

69
00:06:03,260 --> 00:06:04,980
I won't hurt myself again.

70
00:06:11,380 --> 00:06:14,260
[R&F Properties Group]

71
00:06:24,820 --> 00:06:25,380
Mr. Qu,

72
00:06:26,100 --> 00:06:26,860
Miss Shu is here.

73
00:06:27,980 --> 00:06:28,820
Let her in.

74
00:06:29,380 --> 00:06:29,740
Okay.

75
00:06:39,460 --> 00:06:41,540
You came to me
the moment you're discharged.

76
00:06:45,740 --> 00:06:47,660
Looks like I'm quite important.

77
00:06:48,620 --> 00:06:50,060
Stop daydreaming.

78
00:06:51,020 --> 00:06:51,900
I'm just here to tell you

79
00:06:52,340 --> 00:06:53,020
that I quit.

80
00:06:56,980 --> 00:06:58,940
I thought you were here

81
00:06:59,780 --> 00:07:00,820
to relive some memories.

82
00:07:01,780 --> 00:07:02,900
Did you see the photos?

83
00:07:03,740 --> 00:07:04,660
They came out pretty nicely.

84
00:07:09,500 --> 00:07:10,860
Aren't you afraid I will get angry?

85
00:07:11,980 --> 00:07:13,180
The photos came out so well.

86
00:07:13,500 --> 00:07:15,700
If they were uploaded
to some weird websites,

87
00:07:16,660 --> 00:07:17,660
they'll be very popular.

88
00:07:18,620 --> 00:07:20,700
Don't think you can threaten me
with a few photos.

89
00:07:22,060 --> 00:07:23,180
You're the one in the wrong.

90
00:07:23,300 --> 00:07:23,860
Not me.

91
00:07:25,540 --> 00:07:26,980
I will make sure you go to jail.

92
00:07:27,940 --> 00:07:28,860
I'm not even afraid of death.

93
00:07:29,940 --> 00:07:30,780
Would I be afraid of you?

94
00:07:43,420 --> 00:07:45,060
♪SO RE MI♪

95
00:07:46,180 --> 00:07:50,540
♪I can't help thinking♪

96
00:07:51,060 --> 00:07:54,340
♪A happy or sad ending♪

97
00:07:55,820 --> 00:07:59,140
♪Is up to us♪

98
00:07:59,580 --> 00:08:03,340
♪Lovers are always forced to part♪

99
00:08:04,340 --> 00:08:07,260
♪How dramatic♪

100
00:08:08,540 --> 00:08:11,820
♪Doing my best to run to you♪

101
00:08:12,460 --> 00:08:17,500
♪And our happy ending♪

102
00:08:17,980 --> 00:08:20,300
♪If I can meet you again♪

103
00:08:20,620 --> 00:08:22,580
♪And write this story again♪

104
00:08:23,020 --> 00:08:26,540
♪I don't believe in fate♪

105
00:08:27,460 --> 00:08:29,940
♪If I can hug you again♪

106
00:08:30,380 --> 00:08:31,700
♪I don't care♪

107
00:08:31,700 --> 00:08:35,020
♪About the bitter past♪

108
00:08:35,660 --> 00:08:37,780
♪Let all our partings♪

109
00:08:37,780 --> 00:08:39,860
♪Indifference and struggles♪

110
00:08:39,860 --> 00:08:43,140
♪Return to when we met♪

111
00:08:43,780 --> 00:08:46,780
♪As the crowd disappears♪

112
00:08:47,220 --> 00:08:48,540
♪It's still you♪

113
00:08:48,540 --> 00:08:54,900
♪Watching the sunset with me♪

114
00:08:55,940 --> 00:08:58,500
♪If we start again♪

115
00:08:58,500 --> 00:09:00,940
♪Can our ending be changed?♪
